<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt2" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Chinese name","href":"./Template:Chinese_name"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"[[Li (surname 李)|Li]]"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAw">This is a <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Chinese_name" title="Chinese name">Chinese name</a>; the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Chinese_surname" title="Chinese surname">family name</a> is <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Li_(surname_李)" title="Li (surname 李)">Li</a>.</div>
